{"tid":917472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[泛民打手退散]泛民世紀縮沙實錄-梁耀忠放棄代主席職位","createTime":"2018-11-26T12:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T05:06:29.000Z","uid":24140,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9f7efee80169a60ba2966a620d6f964077dece53","tid":917472,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"原本主持立法會主席選舉的梁耀忠臨陣「劈炮」，將主持會議權力交建制派石禮謙，最終完成選舉主席程序，梁君彥當選，令民主派支持者不滿。梁事後解釋，自己並非不想做「醜人」，也認為選主席過程有很多不理想地方，但因自己不能行使主席權力，繼續主持會議意義不大，才交其他議員主持，他為在過程中做得不好道歉。<br />\n梁耀忠任21年立法機關議員，從未主持過任何會議。梁昨在會上表明不願主持會議，只因是資歷最深議員，才由他主持選舉主席的會議。他把主持選舉程序權力交建制派，致石禮謙硬闖，惹來很多民主派人士批評，其維基百科的資料，即遭改為已加入中國共產黨；香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒就在fb貼文指摘：「作為投咗票畀你嘅選民，梁耀忠議員，我真係唔知你發生乜事？」<br />\n梁耀忠事後向傳媒解釋，已盡力按《議事規則》讓議員提問，但很多議員感不滿，希望他留難或不讓梁君彥當選，惟他自問沒有能力做下去，故寧願不繼續主持會議，強調並非不想做「醜人」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投過幾多次反對票<br />\n都唔夠抵呢次既錯呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"a6ace41482ff0d791cc60e621c32b544c00c132a","tid":917472,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T12:17:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/50KBHLI8Jys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F50KBHLI8Jys&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3c22ba42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/50KBHLI8Jys</a>"},{"pid":"fd93559814bd0113ac102125eecbafadf36330c9","tid":917472,"uid":11055,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:18:23.000Z","msg":"2017年6月17日，沙中線8.47億追加撥款以6票之差獲得通過，10名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F162225&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=1aa0908a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2017/06/17/162225</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年3月22日，立法會審議 1131億臨時撥款，在全體泛民議員缺席下，議案只花兩分鐘，由不足十名建制派議員在不記名投票下贊成通過。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180322%2Fbkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=4fc4df51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月26日，工務小組審議17.85億元朗行人天橋撥款，議案以3票之差獲得通過，5名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fv201805261.pdf&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=232d77a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月25日，林卓廷提出就「升降機維修保養對市民安全進行辯論議案」以6票之差未獲通過，7名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fvoting%2Fhc20180525-voting-ec.pdf&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7b8edfb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月31日，建制派「共建粵港澳大灣區」動議順利通過，地方選區輸2票，2名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fvoting%2Fv20180530.pdf&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e84a7093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n順手唔該"},{"pid":"26766e1289ab7de4069f1d9583e0272aa4430af6","tid":917472,"uid":11055,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd93559814bd0113ac102125eecbafadf36330c9","tid":9174