通過，地方選區輸2票，2名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fvoting%2Fv20180530.pdf&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e84a7093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n順手唔該"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:18:44.000Z","msg":"泛民咁多年黎幫左香港咁多，你地香港人有冇感過恩？點解要咁樣對人哥？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/917291\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/917291</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4f9b1ae67b1a70267685b12b176345d43f1856a","tid":917472,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3807aab77e981d78420df2208cb6dd5a73900759","tid":917472,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:19:11.000Z","msg":"白頭佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d34231daa47340c0efa88fbaeb2f0051c3886d","tid":917472,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35d237c9171d9f24fb4cdc0618529e0fc60247b6","tid":917472,"uid":41411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T13:29:15.000Z","msg":"賣港奸賊 屌你老母"},{"pid":"f693cbf6a961c8ca256bbbc38fb4fc09fc21d8f5","tid":917472,"uid":116289,"like":1,"dislike