>http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180322/bkn-20180322090338992-0322_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月26日，工務小組審議17.85億元朗行人天橋撥款，議案以3票之差獲得通過，5名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fresults%2Fv201805261.pdf&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=232d77a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201805261.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月25日，林卓廷提出就「升降機維修保養對市民安全進行辯論議案」以6票之差未獲通過，7名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fhc%2Fvoting%2Fhc20180525-voting-ec.pdf&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7b8edfb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/hc/voting/hc20180525-voting-ec.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年5月31日，建制派「共建粵港澳大灣區」動議順利通過，地方選區輸2票，2名泛民議員缺席未有投票。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr17-18%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fvoting%2Fv20180530.pdf&d=TrLrb1x%2F4u1ojeN89lnOeE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e84a7093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr17-18/chinese/counmtg/voting/v20180530.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n順手唔該"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:08:41.000Z","msg":"你未講埋泛民幫新移民同賓賓姐姐爭取綜援公屋等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a29120cbdf00a5a5b4561b5e0044c4ef0b67b22","tid":917472,"uid":224992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:09:17.000Z","msg":"經典"},{"pid":"ffe3d5444d34980643b88874d98f9ccade98edd2","tid":917472,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T10:52:40.000Z","msg"